description: Returns information about the Detective administrator account for an organization. Can only be called by the organization management account.

nested_items.name: Administrators
nested_items.description: The list of Detective administrator accounts.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account identifier of the Detective administrator account for the organization.

nested_items.name: GraphArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the organization behavior graph.

nested_items.name: DelegationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time when the Detective administrator account was enabled. The value is an ISO8601 formatted string. For example, 2021-08-18T16:35:56.284Z.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are more accounts remaining in the results, then this is the pagination token to use to request the next page of accounts.
